                    <h3 data-uuid="6ef13a33049b48f09f222a057af878e2" class="mod">The North, 1785â€“1860</h3>
                    <p data-uuid="414504fba22b4bbd82147a368e42991c" class="mod">In an age of technology, American inventors transformed life
                        in the United States. They improved textile production and transportation.
                        American inventors also created new and better equipment and manufacturing
                        processes, making the United States an industrial leader.</p>
